name: Garden Arsenal
description:
Garden Arsenal is mod made by MultiTeam; Its all about guns and weapons that shoot vegetables and edible stuff.

Everything from v0.1.0 and v0.2.0 is here, on a new minecraft version!
Fresh and new all hand-written code, combined with all the new and remade assets!
